Requirement:
  * LLVM 3.0 Source Tree or llvm-dev package.

To build PerfScope, use
    $ ./configure --with-llvmsrc=/path/to/llvm/src
    If your obj direction is not the same as source tree location, add
    `--with-llvmobj=/path/to/llvm/obj' to the above
    $ make

To avoid typing the --with-llvmsrc each invocation of configure, you can
first run:
    $ autoconf/AutoRegen.sh 
to customize the configure script.
    
  

